{"tid":1004313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海反傳銷標語現歧義惹議　官方發文致歉兼整改","createTime":"2019-02-01T10:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T10:58:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71f2ae92b6d7f72efa01bd45a97040847e3da259","tid":1004313,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190201/photo/bkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190201172234\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190201172234&h=583cc8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該標語因採用豎式排版，若從左往右讀，意思即大相逕庭。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n設計標語原為協助宣傳引導，惟因排版問題引起誤解，分分鐘就會產生反效果。近日在廣西北海街頭，出現一條「指望傳銷致富，生活沒有出路」的標語，但因採用豎式排版，讀者若從左往右讀，意思就大相逕庭，變成「生活沒有出路，指望傳銷致富」。<br />\n<br />\n據悉有網民發現上述標語排版，並將相關照片上傳至網絡，迅即惹起輿論熱議。北海市公安局銀海分局周四（1月31日）透過社交平台發通報，解釋上述街頭標語的產生和後續處理過程。通報指，相關部門為嚴厲打擊傳銷，遂在相關屋苑懸掛上述標語；但由於標語採用豎式排版，造成閱讀歧義，當局為此表示歉意。 <br />\n<br />\n通報續稱，當局現已將相關宣傳標語版式作出整改，並全面檢查轄區內其他宣傳內容，避免出現同類問題；當局強調徹底剷除傳銷是警方與相關部門職責所在，希望民眾一如既往地支持和監督。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190201/photo/bkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190201172234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190201172234&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=84a34c92\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190201/photo/bkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190201172234</a>"},{"pid":"6363396f0f7c7a7ab9c08536e190350ff907dd2c","tid":1004313,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190201/mobile/bkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190201%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001.html&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsvzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=6aefa7d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190201/mobile/bkn-20190201170447137-0201_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"30810d5ca275327f5c935e767835600fff9bc4d3","tid":1004313,"uid":25656,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"你係北海飲醉酒片車撞死人,你響我暴龍個朵,一啲事都無"},{"pid":"98bded8ac9a83622e93db924a88261f5e18d966f","tid":1004313,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f75de3622c82d7b2351e445c3aba44bf91479408","tid":1004313,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"其實左右讀都冇乜分別"},{"pid":"b22f3396f5f3487aa62c878c98f01d616b181095","tid":1004313,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:57:11.000Z","msg":"直排點讀都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c104b735fb7a634163732772534c42e0456b74","tid":1004313,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30810d5ca275327f5c935e767835600fff9bc4d3","tid":1004313,"uid":25656,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:52:07.000Z","msg":"你係北海飲醉酒片車撞死人,你響我暴龍個朵,一啲事都無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"不過最巧唔好撞啲咁出名架啦"},{"pid":"615d0376af4fa44485fd2f1ff99f687acd0d934d","tid":1004313,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98bded8ac9a83622e93db924a88261f5e18d966f","tid":1004313,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:58:58.000Z","msg":"西貢點解係東面<br />\n東涌點解係西面"}]}